<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>408</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Kum tawmcha I nei tai,
 Buoina phat chawmcha tawh;
 Dahna phat chawmcha mai I nei,
 Paucham phat tawmcha tawh.

[V2]
 2. Thil hihkhelh lungzinna,
 Phat chawmcha sung hina;
 Lei nawpna phat chawmcha I nei,
 Kikhen phat chawmcha tawh.

[V3]
 3. Kumsawt chawlhna munah,
 Kumkhuon umkhawm tai tiu;
 Kumsawt ni lopi vak ta'n a,
 Kumsawt la sa tai tiu.</lyrics>
<title>ONLY A FEW MORE YEARS</title>
</song>